<spush><font:Arial:20>The Trident<spop>

<bitmap:share/misc/help/wpn_blaster.png>Every CAT carries a Trident. The Trident is a powerful but tricky weapon. It always fires 9 shots at once. Because of this, it uses a lot of energy and has a huge recoil, but is able to deal up to 90 points of damage at once. The properties of an individual Trident shot:
